---
title: Margherita Inspired Risotto with Roasted Baby Plum Tomatoes and Pesto Drizzle
description: Our Margherita Inspired Risotto is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R44_W09_UK_V13150-3_Main_low-7cde630d.jpg
